WEBVTT

00:02.803 --> 00:05.939
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

00:05.973 --> 00:07.941
EXCUSE ME.

00:07.975 --> 00:10.244
I ONLY DO ELEVATORS
FOR YOU, KATE.

00:10.278 --> 00:11.645
THIS BETTER BE GOOD.

00:11.679 --> 00:12.980
OKAY. JUST TRUST ME
AND FOLLOW MY LEAD.

00:13.013 --> 00:15.316
WHAT -- ARE YOU TRYING TO
STRANGLE ME?

00:15.349 --> 00:16.817
I JUST WANT YOU
TO MAKE A GOOD IMPRESSION.

00:16.850 --> 00:18.652
WHO EXACTLY
AM I TRYING TO IMPRESS?

00:18.686 --> 00:20.621
NEW BOSS.
SHE'S A REAL BALL-BUSTER --

00:20.654 --> 00:22.790
THINK MARGARET THATCHER
WITH A GUN AND BETTER HAIR,

00:22.823 --> 00:24.292
BUT SHE'S ALSO BRILLIANT,
AND SHE MIGHT BE

00:24.325 --> 00:26.560
THE FIRST FEMALE DIRECTOR
IN THE HISTORY OF THE FBI.

00:26.594 --> 00:28.562
I WOULD LIKE IT
IF SHE TOOK AN INTEREST IN ME,

00:28.596 --> 00:30.564
SO PLEASE JUST BE YOUR NORMAL,
BRILLIANT SELF,

00:30.598 --> 00:32.433
BUT NOT TOO WACKY,
WHAT DO YOU MEAN WACKY?

00:32.466 --> 00:34.068
DON'T.

00:34.102 --> 00:38.172
AH, DR. DANIEL PIERCE,
THIS IS SPECIAL AGENT

00:38.206 --> 00:41.309
IN CHARGE IRENE REARDON
AND JUSTICE KAREN TRENT

00:41.342 --> 00:43.144
OF THE SEVENTH CIRCUIT COURT
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

00:43.177 --> 00:44.378
Irene:
FOR THE TIME BEING.

00:44.412 --> 00:46.046
IN STRICT CONFIDENCE,
I CAN TELL YOU

00:46.080 --> 00:48.582
JUDGE TRENT IS ON THE SHORT LIST
FOR SOLICITOR GENERAL.

00:48.616 --> 00:52.186
FORMAL VETTING BEGINS NEXT WEEK,
BUT ON PRELIMINARY BACKGROUND,

00:52.220 --> 00:53.787
JUDGE TRENT HAS INFORMED US

00:53.821 --> 00:56.190
SHE'S BEEN
RECEIVING DISTURBING LETTERS.

00:56.224 --> 00:57.991
SO WE'RE OPENING
A FORMAL INVESTIGATION.

00:58.025 --> 01:00.328
I KEEP TELLING THEM
THIS ISN'T REALLY NECESSARY.

01:00.361 --> 01:01.595
I'M SURE
HE'S HARMLESS.

01:01.629 --> 01:03.697
BRADY McGRAW.

01:03.731 --> 01:05.466
ARRESTED LAST WINTER
FOR TRESPASSING

01:05.499 --> 01:07.034
ON THE NAVAL STATION
GREAT LAKES

01:07.067 --> 01:08.802
AND CHARGED
WITH DOMESTIC TERRORISM.

01:08.836 --> 01:12.206
HIS BEHAVIOR SEEMED OFF,
SO I ORDERED A PSYCH EVAL.

01:12.240 --> 01:15.042
HE WAS DIAGNOSED
PARANOID SCHIZOPHRENIC.

01:15.075 --> 01:16.477
GIVEN HIS CONDITION,

01:16.510 --> 01:18.712
I SENTENCED HIM TO TREATMENT
INSTEAD OF JAIL.

01:18.746 --> 01:20.548
I'M IMPRESSED.

01:20.581 --> 01:22.082
I WISH MORE JUDGES

01:22.116 --> 01:24.118
HAD SUCH AN ENLIGHTENED VIEW
OF MENTAL ILLNESS.

01:24.152 --> 01:28.021
WELL, HE'S REPAYING THE JUDGE'S
ENLIGHTENMENT BY STALKING HER.

01:28.055 --> 01:30.891
WHICH IS
WHERE YOU COME IN.

01:30.924 --> 01:32.760
AH.

01:35.095 --> 01:38.232
HYPERGRAPHIA.
INTENSE COMPULSION TO WRITE.

01:38.266 --> 01:39.700
DOSTOEVSKY HAD IT.

01:39.733 --> 01:42.703
WELL, THAT'S HARDLY
"THE BROTHERS KARAMAZOV."

01:42.736 --> 01:44.538
[ CHUCKLES ]

01:44.572 --> 01:46.707
THE BUREAU NEEDS
AN EXPERT THREAT ASSESSMENT,

01:46.740 --> 01:48.409
AND AGENT MORETTI TELLS ME

01:48.442 --> 01:50.043
YOU'RE THE MAN TO HELP US
TAKE BRADY OFF THE STREETS.

01:50.077 --> 01:52.546
MAYBE I'M MISSING SOMETHING.
HAS HE COMMITTED A CRIME?

01:52.580 --> 01:54.915
IF YOU DETERMINE
THAT BRADY IS A THREAT, HE HAS.

01:54.948 --> 01:57.385
ARE YOU LOOKING
FOR MY PROFESSIONAL OPINION

01:57.418 --> 01:59.253
OR A RUBBER STAMP?

01:59.287 --> 02:03.056
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT THE SAFETY
OF A FEDERAL JUDGE, DR. PIERCE.

02:03.090 --> 02:04.525
I'M SURE
YOU'LL DO THE RIGHT THING.

02:04.558 --> 02:06.327
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

02:13.301 --> 02:15.403
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

02:15.436 --> 02:18.672
BRADY McGRAW?
AGENT MORETTI, FBI.

02:18.706 --> 02:21.108
Brady: GO AWAY.

02:21.141 --> 02:24.111
JUDGE TRENT
ASKED US TO COME.

02:26.780 --> 02:29.950
Are you enemies
of Ellebra?

02:29.983 --> 02:32.286
NO. NO, BRADY.
WE'RE FRIENDS.

02:37.225 --> 02:39.960
COME IN, QUICK,
BEFORE THEY SEE YOU. QUICK!

02:39.993 --> 02:42.330
[ SIREN WAILS IN DISTANCE ]

02:45.666 --> 02:48.101
WHO ARE
THE ENEMIES OF ELLEBRA?

02:48.135 --> 02:49.703
THE TURLOCKS.

02:49.737 --> 02:52.973
THEY'RE ALWAYS AFTER ME,
BUT WE'RE SAFE IN HERE.

02:53.006 --> 02:54.642
MAYBE THEY SAW YOU COMING.

02:54.675 --> 02:57.811
I'M GONNA ACTIVATE THE JAMMERS
TO BLOCK THEIR PROBES

02:57.845 --> 03:00.481
SO THAT THEY CAN'T HEAR US.

03:00.514 --> 03:02.283
THEY GET STATIC.

03:02.316 --> 03:04.017
IT HURTS THEIR EARS,

03:04.051 --> 03:06.654
BUT THEY DESERVE IT BECAUSE
THEY'RE ALWAYS SPYING ON ME.

03:06.687 --> 03:08.689
[ STATIC ]

03:10.991 --> 03:12.660
THAT'S
A BEAUTIFUL PAINTING.

03:15.195 --> 03:18.432
NO. YOU CAN'T LOOK AT THIS.
YOU DON'T HAVE PROPER CLEARANCE.

03:18.466 --> 03:20.834
IT LOOKS
JUST LIKE JUDGE TRENT.

03:20.868 --> 03:22.102
NO. IT'S NOT HER.

03:22.135 --> 03:25.673
IT'S OKAY.
WE UNDERSTAND.

03:27.341 --> 03:30.177
YOU HAVE TO
PROTECT HER IDENTITY.

03:30.210 --> 03:32.846
YOU KNOW ABOUT THAT?

03:37.551 --> 03:39.253
YOU CAN TRUST US, BRADY.

03:40.721 --> 03:42.656
JUST LIKE
YOU TRUST THE HEALER.

03:44.358 --> 03:47.194
SH-SH-SHE'S
THE ONLY OTHER ONE I'VE TOLD.

03:49.162 --> 03:52.065
H-HOW DID YOU
LEARN THE JUDGE'S SECRET?

03:52.099 --> 03:53.501
DID SHE TELL YOU?

03:53.534 --> 03:55.869
I RECEIVED A CODED MESSAGE
FROM ELLEBRA.

03:55.903 --> 03:57.705
IT'S HER HOME PLANET.

03:57.738 --> 04:00.040
THEY TOLD ME
THAT SHE'D BEEN SENT HERE

04:00.073 --> 04:02.310
TO AVENGE ALL INJUSTICE
IN OUR WORLD.

04:06.213 --> 04:08.882
HER REAL NAME
IS NEMESIS.

04:08.916 --> 04:10.718
YES.

04:10.751 --> 04:12.520
SO SHE'S AN ENEMY.

04:13.421 --> 04:15.456
NO.

04:16.223 --> 04:17.725
NO, SHE DOESN'T UNDERSTAND.

04:17.758 --> 04:19.059
SHE DOESN'T UNDERSTAND.

04:19.092 --> 04:20.894
I'LL EXPLAIN.

04:20.928 --> 04:23.431
UM, THE GREEK PERSONIFICATION
OF -- OF JUSTICE

04:23.464 --> 04:25.733
WASN'T A BLINDFOLDED VIRGIN
WITH SCALES.

04:25.766 --> 04:28.068
IT WAS NEMESIS,
A FIERCE WARRIOR,

04:28.101 --> 04:30.738
WHO EXACTED VENGEANCE WITH
HER SWORD OF JUSTICE, RIGHT?

04:30.771 --> 04:33.240
YES.

04:33.273 --> 04:35.909
THIS IS THE SWORD OF ELLEBRA.

04:35.943 --> 04:38.078
THEY'VE ENTRUSTED IT WITH ME,

04:38.111 --> 04:40.013
TO HELP THE JUDGE
ON HER MISSION.

04:40.047 --> 04:41.315
WHAT MISSION?

04:41.349 --> 04:42.916
TO SAVE EARTH.

04:44.452 --> 04:47.555
THE ELLEBRANS HAVE HAD PEACE
FOR THOUSANDS OF YEARS,

04:47.588 --> 04:51.024
AND NOW THEY WANT TO HELP US
EVOLVE OUT OF WAR AND VIOLENCE.

04:51.058 --> 04:52.593
SO THEY SENT NEMESIS

04:52.626 --> 04:55.763
TO AVENGE ALL WRONG
AND VANQUISH ALL EVILDOERS.

04:55.796 --> 04:59.266
AND I'M DOING
EVERYTHING THAT I CAN

04:59.299 --> 05:01.268
TO HELP HER
COMPLETE THE MISSION.

05:01.301 --> 05:03.437
LIKE
WRITING HER LETTERS.

05:03.471 --> 05:05.205
YES.

05:05.238 --> 05:09.843
SHE'S ALL ALONE ON --
ON AN ALIEN PLANET.

05:09.877 --> 05:13.514
I WANTED HER TO KNOW
THAT I WAS HER FRIEND.

05:14.615 --> 05:18.085
THAT'S GOOD, BRADY,
BUT YOU SHOULD KNOW

05:18.118 --> 05:22.089
THAT JUDGE TRENT WASN'T
COMFORTED BY YOUR LETTERS.

05:22.122 --> 05:23.724
SHE WAS FRIGHTENED.

05:23.757 --> 05:25.559
NO.

05:25.593 --> 05:27.094
I NEVER MEANT TO SCARE HER.

05:27.127 --> 05:29.763
I JUST WANTED HER TO KNOW
THAT I WAS ON HER SIDE.

05:30.998 --> 05:33.767
SAVING THE WORLD
IS A LONELY JOB.

05:33.801 --> 05:37.371
BRADY, ARE YOU --
ARE YOU SEEING A DOCTOR?

05:38.972 --> 05:40.641
YOU'RE JUST
LIKE ALL THE REST.

05:40.674 --> 05:42.610
YOU PRETEND TO UNDERSTAND,
BUT YOU JUST WANT TO LOCK ME UP,

05:42.643 --> 05:45.078
SHOVE ME DOWN,
AND PUT PILLS IN MY THROAT.

05:45.112 --> 05:47.481
NO. NO, I WOULD NEVER
DO THAT TO YOU, BRADY.

05:47.515 --> 05:52.119
BUT YOU'RE CARRYING A VERY
HEAVY BURDEN ALL BY YOURSELF.

05:52.152 --> 05:53.787
AND MEDICATION
CAN BE HELPFUL.

05:53.821 --> 05:55.989
THERE ARE NEW PILLS
WITH FEWER SIDE EFFECTS.

05:56.023 --> 06:00.661
IF I TAKE PILLS,
THE SIGNALS GET ALL SCRAMBLED,

06:00.694 --> 06:04.865
I CAN'T RECEIVE MESSAGES,
ELLEBRA VANISHES.

06:06.366 --> 06:09.236
AND THEN I'M ALL ALONE.

06:13.340 --> 06:16.544
Daniel: BRADY McGRAW SEES YOU
AS THE SAVIOR OF THE PLANET.

06:16.577 --> 06:18.779
HE THINKS
YOU'RE A SUPERHERO WITH --

06:18.812 --> 06:21.949
WITH A DOUBLE IDENTITY LITERALLY
SENT HERE TO SAVE EARTH.

06:23.316 --> 06:26.620
SOUNDS LIKE I'M CLARK KENT,
FROM ELLEBRA INSTEAD OF KRYPTON.

06:26.654 --> 06:28.188
Daniel:
SCHIZOPHRENICS

06:28.221 --> 06:31.191
OFTEN CONFLATE POP CULTURE
INTO THEIR DELUSIONS.

06:31.224 --> 06:33.494
SO, WHAT, THIS --
THIS KOOK IS LEX LUTHOR?

06:33.527 --> 06:34.528
NO, NO. NOT AT ALL.

06:34.562 --> 06:36.129
NO, ON THE CONTRARY,

06:36.163 --> 06:38.165
HE SEES HIMSELF AS --
AS YOUR WIFE'S PROTECTOR.

06:38.198 --> 06:40.868
HE'D RATHER DIE
THAN HAVE HARM COME TO HER.

06:40.901 --> 06:44.237
THAT'S A RELIEF, RIGHT?
MAYBE NOW EVERYONE CAN RELAX.

06:45.739 --> 06:49.042
LOOK, I'M A REAL-ESTATE
DEVELOPER, NOT A COP,

06:49.076 --> 06:51.044
BUT I'VE GOT A PRETTY GOOD
[BLEEP] DETECTOR.

06:51.078 --> 06:52.880
AND RIGHT NOW,
IT'S RINGING OFF THE HOOK.

06:52.913 --> 06:56.349
A DISTURBED GUY
HAS DELUSIONS ABOUT MY WIFE,

06:56.383 --> 06:57.751
HE'S RANTING ABOUT SWORDS,

06:57.785 --> 06:59.953
AND YOU WANT TO
LEAVE HIM OUT ON THE STREET?

06:59.987 --> 07:01.689
THAT'S THE LAW, HONEY.

07:01.722 --> 07:03.891
IF HE HASN'T COMMITTED A CRIME,
HE CAN'T BE LOCKED UP.

07:03.924 --> 07:05.225
THEN HE SHOULD BE
HOSPITALIZED.

07:05.258 --> 07:07.828
YOU CAN'T FORCE BRADY
INTO TREATMENT

07:07.861 --> 07:09.563
JUST BECAUSE
HE MAKES YOU UNCOMFORTABLE.

07:09.597 --> 07:11.565
HE'S GOT RIGHTS, INCLUDING
THE RIGHT NOT TO BE MEDICATED

07:11.599 --> 07:14.067
OR COMMITTED
AGAINST HIS WILL.

07:14.101 --> 07:15.736
Kate: IF IT WOULD
MAKE YOU FEEL BETTER,

07:15.769 --> 07:18.338
I COULD HAVE THE MARSHALS'
SERVICE PUT A CAR OUTSIDE,

07:18.371 --> 07:19.439
JUST FOR A FEW DAYS.

07:19.473 --> 07:20.874
[ SCOFFS ]
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

07:20.908 --> 07:22.843
NO. I -- DO YOU REMEMBER
THE O'BANNION TRIAL?

07:22.876 --> 07:24.277
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:24.311 --> 07:27.247
THE IRISH MOB SUPPOSEDLY
HAD A CONTRACT OUT ON ME,

07:27.280 --> 07:29.249
AND I SUDDENLY
HAD A PACK OF FEDERAL AGENTS

07:29.282 --> 07:32.085
TROTTING BEHIND ME
ON MY MORNING RUN.

07:32.119 --> 07:35.422
I FELT LIKE AN IDIOT.
THANKS, BUT NO THANKS.

07:35.455 --> 07:38.325
I JUST WANT TO
GET ON WITH MY LIFE.

07:41.128 --> 07:43.396
[ SIGHS ] I WISH
I COULD HAVE HELPED BRADY.

07:43.430 --> 07:45.566
YOU STOPPED THE FEDS
FROM LOCKING HIM UP.

07:45.599 --> 07:46.767
IT SOUNDS LIKE A WIN.

07:46.800 --> 07:48.936
HE NEEDS THERAPY,
MEDICATION.

07:48.969 --> 07:50.070
POT, MEET KETTLE.

07:50.103 --> 07:53.073
I'M NOT A HYPOCRITE,
NATALIE.

07:53.106 --> 07:55.743
I NEVER SAID THAT MEDICATION
CAN'T BE A LIFESAVER.

07:55.776 --> 07:56.944
FOR EVERYONE BUT YOU.

07:56.977 --> 07:58.278
I'M FINE.

07:58.311 --> 08:01.448
I'VE GOT MY ROUTINES,
I'VE GOT LEWICKI.

08:01.481 --> 08:04.084
METHINKS THE NEUROPSYCHIATRIST
DOTH PROTEST TOO MUCH.

08:04.117 --> 08:07.721
I AM COMPLETELY FUNCTIONAL.
BRADY'S LOST IN HIS DELUSIONS.

08:07.755 --> 08:09.289
YOU HALLUCINATE.

08:09.322 --> 08:11.158
YEAH, AND AS
YOU'RE ALWAYS POINTING OUT,

08:11.191 --> 08:13.961
SOMETIMES MY HALLUCINATIONS HELP
ME ACCESS MY UNCONSCIOUS MIND.

08:13.994 --> 08:15.963
IT'S COME IN HANDY LATELY.

08:15.996 --> 08:18.766
IT ALSO PREVENTS YOU
FROM LEADING A NORMAL LIFE...

08:20.067 --> 08:21.602
...FROM
MAKING REAL FRIENDS.

08:21.635 --> 08:25.138
WELL, MAYBE
I LIKE THE FRIENDS I GOT.

08:25.172 --> 08:27.174
[ Kate: DANIEL. ]

08:30.010 --> 08:32.980
DAVID TRENT
CAME HOME TONIGHT

08:33.013 --> 08:34.915
AND FOUND HIS WIFE
STABBED TO DEATH.

08:34.948 --> 08:36.984
THERE'S
NO FORENSIC EVIDENCE YET,

08:37.017 --> 08:40.821
BUT THE WORKING ASSUMPTION
IS THAT BRADY McGRAW DID IT.

08:40.854 --> 08:42.990
I NEED TO
SEE THAT CRIME SCENE.

08:44.024 --> 08:45.659
Kate: I'M DON'T KNOW
IF THIS IS A GOOD IDEA.

08:45.693 --> 08:47.460
THEY SAID
IT'S A BLOODY MESS INSIDE.

08:47.494 --> 08:49.963
I NEED TO SEE IT.
THERE MAY BE EVIDENCE
THAT EXONERATES BRADY.

08:49.997 --> 08:51.364
THIS ISMR. TRENT --

08:51.398 --> 08:52.966
YOU SAID
HE WOULDI-I --RT HER.

08:53.000 --> 08:54.267
YOU TOLD HER SHE WAS SAFE,
AND NOW SHE'S DEAD!

08:54.301 --> 08:55.969
GET HIM OUT OF HERE,
AGENT MORETTI.

08:56.003 --> 08:57.638
I MIGHT --
MAYBE I CAN HELP.

08:57.671 --> 08:58.972
YOU'VE DONE ENOUGH FOR ONE DAY.
GET HIM OUT OF HERE!

08:59.006 --> 09:00.307
IF I CAN JUST --

09:00.340 --> 09:01.909
[ SIGHS ]

09:10.751 --> 09:12.152
Kate:
I HEARD THE BRIEFING.

09:12.185 --> 09:14.087
THE TASK FORCE
HASN'T FOUND BRADY McGRAW

09:14.121 --> 09:16.089
OR ANY FORENSIC EVIDENCE
AGAINST HIM.

09:16.123 --> 09:17.658
THANKS FOR THE UPDATE,

09:17.691 --> 09:20.027
BUT I'M WELL AWARE OF
WHERE THIS INVESTIGATION STANDS.

09:20.060 --> 09:22.596
I'D LIKE YOUR PERMISSION
TO PURSUE OTHER SUSPECTS.

09:22.630 --> 09:25.198
OKAY,
YOU'VE GOT MY ATTENTION.

09:25.232 --> 09:26.834
WHAT OTHER SUSPECTS?

09:26.867 --> 09:28.836
SHE MADE
A LOT OF ENEMIES.

09:28.869 --> 09:31.304
SHE SENTENCED HALF
OF THE SINALOA CARTEL TO DEATH.

09:31.338 --> 09:33.607
SHE APPROVED
THE REZONING OF CABRINI-GREEN

09:33.641 --> 09:36.376
INTO COMMERCIAL DEVELOPMENT
INSTEAD OF LOW-INCOME HOUSING --

09:36.409 --> 09:38.111
[BLEEP]
A LOT PEOPLE OFF.

09:38.145 --> 09:40.547
JUST LAST YEAR, THE IRISH MOB
PUT A BOUNTY ON HER HEAD.

09:40.580 --> 09:42.883
AGENT MORETTI,
I APPRECIATE YOUR INITIATIVE,

09:42.916 --> 09:44.885
BUT JUDGE TRENT
WAS BRUTALLY STABBED TO DEATH

09:44.918 --> 09:46.119
IN HER OWN HOME.

09:46.153 --> 09:48.121
IT HARDLY LOOKS LIKE
A PROFESSIONAL HIT.

09:48.155 --> 09:50.590
WHAT IT DOES LOOK LIKE
IS THE WORK OF A DISTURBED MAN

09:50.624 --> 09:52.559
WHOM DR. PIERCE
CLAIMED WAS NOT A THREAT.

09:52.592 --> 09:55.328
BUT IT IS POSSIBLE
THAT BRADY'S NOT THE KILLER.

09:55.362 --> 09:56.897
YOUR PET EXPERT
SCREWED THE POOCH.

09:56.930 --> 09:58.999
BECAUSE OF HIM,
JUDGE TRENT IS DEAD!

09:59.032 --> 10:00.367
BECAUSE OF THAT,

10:00.400 --> 10:02.502
I JUST GOT AN EARFUL
FROM THE DIRECTOR HIMSELF,

10:02.535 --> 10:04.905
AFTER HE GOT AN EARFUL
FROM THE WHITE HOUSE.

10:04.938 --> 10:07.340
NOT EXACTLY
THE IMPRESSION I WANTED TO MAKE

10:07.374 --> 10:09.142
IN MY FIRST WEEK
IN THIS JOB.

10:09.176 --> 10:12.579
NOT EXACTLY THE IMPRESSION
I WANTED TO MAKE ON YOU, EITHER.

10:13.647 --> 10:17.284
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:17.317 --> 10:18.852
THEN YOU'LL UNDERSTAND

10:18.886 --> 10:20.721
WHY I'M GOING TO MUDDLE THROUGH
THIS INVESTIGATION

10:20.754 --> 10:22.923
WITHOUT
YOUR INVALUABLE ASSISTANCE.

10:25.058 --> 10:26.393
YES, MA'AM.

10:26.426 --> 10:29.529
CRAZY CRIME --
MUST BE A CRAZY KILLER.

10:29.562 --> 10:32.165
NO WAY A SANE PERSON
WOULD DO SOMETHING LIKE THAT,

10:32.199 --> 10:34.167
SO IT'S GOT TO BE
A SCHIZOPHRENIC.

10:34.201 --> 10:35.602
YOU'RE OVER-IDENTIFYING
WITH BRADY.

10:35.635 --> 10:37.170
YEAH, THAT'S
'CAUSE HE'S WRONGLY ACCUSED.

10:37.204 --> 10:38.906
DANIEL, JUST BECAUSE
YOU'VE NEVER BEEN VIOLENT

10:38.939 --> 10:40.908
DOESN'T MEAN THE SAME IS TRUE
OF ALL SCHIZOPHRENICS.

10:40.941 --> 10:44.745
WELL, ALL OF BRADY'S DELUSIONS
ABOUT THE JUDGE WERE POSITIVE.

10:44.778 --> 10:47.047
HE VENERATED THE WOMAN.
HE HAD NO REASON TO HURT HER.

10:47.080 --> 10:48.682
AND THERE'S NO EVIDENCE
THAT HE DID.

10:48.716 --> 10:50.650
WELL, IF YOU'RE SO SURE
THAT HE'S INNOCENT,

10:50.684 --> 10:52.452
WOULDN'T FINDING HIM
AND EXONERATING HIM

10:52.485 --> 10:54.822
BE BETTER THAN RANTING TO ME
ABOUT THE INJUSTICE OF IT ALL?

10:54.855 --> 10:56.289
YES.

10:56.323 --> 10:58.591
EXCEPT FOR THE FACT
THAT I'M PERSONA NON GRATA

10:58.625 --> 11:00.060
AT THE FBI
AT THE MOMENT.

11:00.093 --> 11:01.628
BESIDES,
HOW WOULD I FIND HIM

11:01.661 --> 11:04.965
WHEN 100 FEDERAL AGENTS
AND THE CHICAGO P.D. CAN'T?

11:04.998 --> 11:10.637
BECAUSE YOU CAN UNDERSTAND HIM
IN A WAY THAT NO COP CAN.

11:10.670 --> 11:16.143
WHERE DO YOU FIND ANSWERS
TO PROBLEMS YOU CAN'T SOLVE?

11:16.176 --> 11:18.145
You are not
supposed to be here.

11:18.178 --> 11:19.479
I think I know
how to find Brady.

11:19.512 --> 11:21.148
DANIEL, WE WERE
KICKED OFF THE CASE.

11:21.181 --> 11:22.950
THE KEY IS UNDERSTANDING
HIS DELUSIONS.

11:22.983 --> 11:24.617
REMEMBER "THE HEALER"?

11:24.651 --> 11:26.353
HE TRUSTED HER.
HE CONFIDED IN HER.

11:26.386 --> 11:29.222
IF WE CAN FIGURE OUT WHO SHE IS,
MAYBE SHE CAN HELP US FIND HIM.

11:29.256 --> 11:31.424
FOR ALL WE KNOW,
SHE IS FROM THE PLANET ELLEBRA.

11:31.458 --> 11:33.927
SO, WAIT? YOU WANT ME
TO TRACK DOWN AN ALIEN?

11:33.961 --> 11:37.164
NO, IN BRADY'S MIND, JUDGE TRENT
WAS AN ALIEN, BUT SHE'S REAL.

11:37.197 --> 11:38.531
THE HEALER MUST BE, TOO.

11:38.565 --> 11:40.433
SO, WHERE SHOULD START?
THE HUBBLE TELESCOPE?

11:40.467 --> 11:42.469
THE JUDGE ORDERED HIM
INTO PSYCHIATRIC CARE.

11:42.502 --> 11:44.371
"THE HEALER"
MAY BE ONE OF HIS DOCTORS.

11:44.404 --> 11:46.373
AGENTS TALKED TO BRADY'S
SHRINK AT CEDAR HEIGHTS.

11:46.406 --> 11:48.041
HE HAS NO IDEA
WHERE HE IS.

11:48.075 --> 11:51.011
OKAY, SO, THERE'S LOTS
OF CAREGIVERS IN A HOSPITAL --

11:51.044 --> 11:53.046
ORDERLIES, NURSES,
SOCIAL WORKERS.

11:53.080 --> 11:54.714
WE CAN'T
JUST MARCH INTO THE HOSPITAL

11:54.748 --> 11:57.017
AND START INTERVIEWING
500 EMPLOYEES.

11:57.050 --> 11:58.651
WHAT PLANET ARE YOU FROM,

11:58.685 --> 12:00.187
AND WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
WITH THE REAL KATE MORETTI?

12:02.489 --> 12:04.758
Ellen: WHAT DOES THE FBI WANT
WITH BRADY?

12:04.792 --> 12:06.159
WELL, WE'RE TRYING TO
LOCATE HIM.

12:06.193 --> 12:07.460
WHY?
WHAT DO YOU THINK HE DID?

12:07.494 --> 12:09.029
THEY THINK HE STABBED
A FEDERAL JUDGE.

12:09.062 --> 12:10.530
OH, THERE'S NO WAY.
BRADY'S GENTLE.

12:10.563 --> 12:12.265
AND HE'S FREAKED OUT
BY THE SIGHT OF BLOOD.

12:12.299 --> 12:13.967
YOU CAN'T EVEN
GET NEAR HIM WITH A SYRINGE

12:14.001 --> 12:15.268
UNLESS HE HAS
A VALIUM IN HIM.

12:15.302 --> 12:17.637
HE'S ALWAYS
BEEN LIKE THAT.

12:17.670 --> 12:19.672
SOUNDS LIKE
YOU KNOW HIM PRETTY WELL.

12:19.706 --> 12:21.975
HE'S KIND OF
A FREQUENT FLYER AROUND HERE.

12:22.009 --> 12:23.877
HE'S BEEN IN AND OUT
OF TREATMENT A DOZEN TIMES

12:23.911 --> 12:25.178
SINCE HE WAS 17.

12:25.212 --> 12:26.980
HE'S A SWEET KID
WHEN HE'S ON HIS MEDS.

12:27.014 --> 12:29.482
WELL, APPARENTLY,
HE'S NOT ON THEM NOW.

12:29.516 --> 12:31.218
I KNOW.
I SPOKE WITH HIM LAST WEEK.

12:31.251 --> 12:32.752
YOU KEPT IN TOUCH
AFTER HE WAS DISCHARGED.

12:32.786 --> 12:34.654
HE DOESN'T
HAVE ANYONE ELSE.

12:34.687 --> 12:36.289
BOTH HIS PARENTS ARE DEAD,

12:36.323 --> 12:38.892
AND HE SCARES NEW PEOPLE OFF
WITH HIS DELUSIONS ABOUT ALIENS.

12:38.926 --> 12:40.660
HE'S LUCKY
TO HAVE A FRIEND LIKE YOU.

12:40.693 --> 12:42.595
SOME FRIEND I WAS.

12:42.629 --> 12:44.164
I KNEW HE WAS DECOMPENSATING,
AND I COULDN'T CONVINCE HIM

12:44.197 --> 12:46.666
TO GET BACK ON HIS MEDS
OR ADMIT HIMSELF.

12:46.699 --> 12:48.936
I WISH
I COULD HAVE HELPED.

12:48.969 --> 12:50.270
YOU CAN HELP HIM NOW.

12:50.303 --> 12:51.771
[ SIGHS ]

12:51.805 --> 12:55.075
YOU MEAN I CAN HELP YOU.
YOU WANT ME TO TURN HIM IN.

12:55.108 --> 12:56.409
DO YOU KNOW
WHERE HE IS?

12:56.443 --> 12:57.911
IF I DID,
I PROBABLY WOULDN'T TELL YOU.

12:57.945 --> 13:00.513
I'VE SEEN HOW COPS
TREAT THE MENTALLY ILL.

13:00.547 --> 13:02.315
ONE TIME BRADY
WAS BROUGHT IN BY CPD,

13:02.349 --> 13:04.251
THEY PEPPER-SPRAYED HIM
FOR NO REASON.

13:04.284 --> 13:05.819
ELLEN, I'M NOT A COP.
I'M A PHYSICIAN.

13:05.853 --> 13:08.255
I KNOW HOW TO
BRING BRADY IN SAFELY.

13:08.288 --> 13:10.023
AND ONCE WE DO THAT,
IT MAY BE POSSIBLE

13:10.057 --> 13:11.825
TO GET HIM MANDATED
BACK INTO TREATMENT.

13:11.859 --> 13:14.094
NO JAIL?

13:14.127 --> 13:15.162
NOT IF I CAN HELP IT.

13:18.065 --> 13:21.935
THERE'S AN ABANDONED WAREHOUSE
OFF TORRENCE AVENUE.

13:21.969 --> 13:24.204
I PICKED HIM UP THERE ONCE
WHEN HE CALLED ME FOR HELP.

13:24.237 --> 13:26.606
HE SAID
IT'S A PORTAL TO ELLEBRA.

13:29.843 --> 13:33.613
WHEN WE GET THERE, YOU HAVE TO
LET ME TAKE THE LEAD.

13:33.646 --> 13:35.148
DANIEL, WE CAN'T
GO PICK HIM UP ON OUR OWN.

13:35.182 --> 13:36.149
WHY NOT?

13:36.183 --> 13:37.717
BECAUSE IT'S ONE THING

13:37.750 --> 13:39.052
FOR ME TO INTERVIEW
A BUNCH OF HOSPITAL EMPLOYEES.

13:39.086 --> 13:40.153
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT
A FUGITIVE HERE,

13:40.187 --> 13:41.488
MAYBE ARMED,
MAYBE DANGEROUS.

13:41.521 --> 13:43.556
HE'S NOT DANGEROUS.

13:43.590 --> 13:45.125
I KNOW YOU THINK THAT,

13:45.158 --> 13:46.726
BUT IF YOU'RE WRONG
AND I HAVEN'T FOLLOW PROCEDURE,

13:46.759 --> 13:48.295
IF I DON'T
HI KNOW, I KNOW.--

13:48.328 --> 13:50.463
YOU'LL GET IN EVEN BIGGER
TROUBLE WITH YOUR NEW BOSS.

13:50.497 --> 13:51.999
WHAT I WAS GOING TO SAY

13:52.032 --> 13:54.667
WAS IF ANYTHING HAPPENED TO YOU,
IT'D BE MY FAULT.

13:54.701 --> 13:56.169
I'D NEVER FORGIVE MYSELF.

13:58.105 --> 14:01.174
Irene: YOU CONDUCT A ROGUE
INVESTIGATION WITH A CIVILIAN,

14:01.208 --> 14:03.843
AFTER I SPECIFICALLY
ORDERED YOU NOT TO,

14:03.877 --> 14:05.578
AND NOW YOU WALTZ IN HERE

14:05.612 --> 14:07.747
AND ANNOUNCE YOU THINK YOU KNOW
WHERE BRADY McGRAW IS.

14:07.780 --> 14:09.082
YES.

14:09.116 --> 14:11.284
YOU'VE GOT BRASS ONES,
AGENT MORETTI.

14:11.318 --> 14:12.485
I'LL GIVE YOU THAT.

14:13.786 --> 14:16.089
HOW SURE ARE YOU
THAT BRADY McGRAW

14:16.123 --> 14:17.590
IS AT THIS WAREHOUSE?

14:17.624 --> 14:20.260
SCHIZOPHRENICS ARE CREATURES
OF HABIT AND RITUAL.

14:20.293 --> 14:23.196
AT A TIME OF STRESS,
HE'D RETREAT TO THE FAMILIAR.

14:23.230 --> 14:25.598
WELL,
THANK YOU, DR. PIERCE.

14:25.632 --> 14:28.201
YOU HAVE TO
LET ME BRING HIM IN.

14:28.235 --> 14:29.903
YOU'RE NOT
A TRAINED FIELD AGENT.

14:29.937 --> 14:32.272
BRADY McGRAW
IS MENTALLY ILL.

14:32.305 --> 14:34.741
MY TRAINING
IS EXACTLY THE KIND YOU NEED.

14:39.346 --> 14:41.181
JUST DON'T SCREW UP AGAIN.

14:47.420 --> 14:50.123
BRADY?

14:50.157 --> 14:53.526
IT'S DOCTOR PIERCE.

14:53.560 --> 14:55.428
BRADY: Go away.
You shouldn't be here.

14:57.264 --> 14:59.866
BRADY, PLEASE COME OUT.
WE NEED TO TALK.

15:05.605 --> 15:07.374
Who are they?

15:07.407 --> 15:09.642
THEY'RE --
THEY'RE FEDERAL AGENTS.

15:09.676 --> 15:11.811
THEY'RE HERE
TO PROTECT YOU.

15:11.844 --> 15:13.213
I DON'T BELIEVE THAT.

15:13.246 --> 15:15.215
TRUST ME, BRADY.

15:15.248 --> 15:17.450
NO ONE WANTS TO
SEE YOU GET HURT.

15:36.003 --> 15:37.604
WEAPON!

15:37.637 --> 15:38.838
YOU LIED TO ME?

15:38.871 --> 15:40.340
BRADY, NO!

15:40.373 --> 15:42.742
[ SCREAMING ]

15:42.775 --> 15:44.077
OH, GOD!

15:44.111 --> 15:46.146
[ SCREAMING ]

15:59.592 --> 16:01.128
WE ALREADY HAVE A TEAM OF AGENTS
IINTERROGATING HIM..

16:01.161 --> 16:02.996
HE'S ILL.
HE WON'T TALK TO THEM.

16:03.030 --> 16:05.398
ON THE CONTRARY,
HE'S TALKING A GREAT DEAL.

16:05.432 --> 16:07.467
IN FACT,
HE'S MADE A FULL CONFESSION.

16:07.500 --> 16:10.970
I APPRECIATE YOUR HELP
LOCATING BRADY.

16:11.004 --> 16:12.205
I REALLY DO.

16:12.239 --> 16:14.407
BUT YOUR ROLE IN THIS CASE
IS FINISHED.

16:14.441 --> 16:17.577
TH-- IT JUST -- THAT DOESN'T --
A CONFESSION DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

16:17.610 --> 16:19.079
UNLESS BRADY
ACTUALLY DID IT.

16:19.112 --> 16:20.580
NO, NO, NO.
I DON'T BELIEVE THAT.

16:20.613 --> 16:24.017
OH, BELIEVE IT, DR. PIERCE.
THE MURDER WEAPON.

16:24.051 --> 16:25.418
COMPLETE WITH BLOODY
FINGERPRINTS ON THE HANDLE,

16:25.452 --> 16:28.155
WHICH WILL
MATCH BRADY McGRAW'S.

16:28.188 --> 16:29.656
YOU --
YOU CAN'T BE SURE.

16:29.689 --> 16:31.724
HE'S THE ONE WHO TOLD US
WHERE THE KNIFE WAS HIDDEN.

16:31.758 --> 16:34.927
Brady:
I STABBED HER, OVER AND OVER,

16:34.961 --> 16:38.398
AND I DIDN'T STOP
UNTIL SHE WAS DEAD.

16:38.431 --> 16:40.400
OF COURSE HE CONFESSED.

16:40.433 --> 16:41.968
IT'S CALLED
IMAGINATION INFLATION.

16:42.001 --> 16:44.104
YOU TELL A SCHIZOPHRENIC
THE SAME STORY ENOUGH TIMES

16:44.137 --> 16:45.472
AND HE STARTS
TO BELIEVE IT.

16:45.505 --> 16:47.040
THOSE AGENTS
TOLD HIM OVER AND OVER AGAIN

16:47.074 --> 16:48.441
THAT THEY KNOW
HE DID IT.

16:48.475 --> 16:50.443
DANIEL, IT WAS
A BY-THE-BOOK INTERROGATION,

16:50.477 --> 16:52.445
BRADY WAS OFFERED FOOD,
WATER.

16:52.479 --> 16:54.447
HE WAS NEVER YELLED AT
OR THREATENED.

16:54.481 --> 16:56.116
HE SHOULD HAVE
HAD AN ATTORNEY PRESENT.

16:56.149 --> 16:58.418
THEY MIRANDIZED HIM TWICE.
HE DENIED REPRESENTATION.

16:58.451 --> 17:00.153
WELL, OF COURSE,
BECAUSE HE SAID,

17:00.187 --> 17:02.122
"THE ONLY LAW
IS THE LAW OF ELLEBRA."

17:02.155 --> 17:04.457
THE COURT WILL APPOINT A LAWYER
AT ARRAIGNMENT.

17:04.491 --> 17:06.526
I'M SURE THE ISSUE OF BRADY'S
COMPETENCE WILL BE RAISED.

17:06.559 --> 17:07.860
THAT'S GREAT.

17:07.894 --> 17:09.629
AN OVERWORKED,
UNDERPAID PUBLIC DEFENDER,

17:09.662 --> 17:11.964
WHO PROBABLY WON'T HAVE ENOUGH
TIME TO READ THE CASE FILE

17:11.998 --> 17:13.166
BEFORE
PLEADING BRADY OUT.

17:13.200 --> 17:14.934
DANIEL, ENOUGH.

17:14.967 --> 17:17.137
THE BLOODY FINGERPRINTS ON
THE MURDER WEAPON ARE BRADY'S.

17:17.170 --> 17:20.307
THE JUDGE'S BLOOD
WAS ON HIS CLOTHES.

17:20.340 --> 17:22.642
THERE HAS TO BE
ANOTHER EXPLANATION.

17:22.675 --> 17:25.145
LISTEN, I REALIZE THAT
THIS IS HARD FOR YOU TO ACCEPT,

17:25.178 --> 17:26.546
BUT BRADY DID IT.

17:26.579 --> 17:28.981
[ SIGHS ]

17:29.015 --> 17:31.017
[ PIANO PLAYING ]

17:34.121 --> 17:39.826
Nemesis:
THAT'S PRETTY GLOOMY.

17:39.859 --> 17:41.994
HOW ABOUT SOMETHING
A LITTLE MORE UP-TEMPO?

17:42.028 --> 17:44.997
YOU'RE NOT REAL.

17:45.031 --> 17:47.500
YOU'RE NOT EVEN MY
HALLUCINATION -- YOU'RE BRADY'S.

17:47.534 --> 17:50.670
WHAT'S A SHARED DELUSION
AMONG FRIENDS?

17:50.703 --> 17:52.972
AND BRADY NEEDS A FRIEND
RIGHT NOW.

17:53.005 --> 17:56.343
HE'S ALONE IN JAIL,

17:56.376 --> 17:58.010
SLOWLY LOSING
WHAT'S LEFT OF HIS SANITY.

17:58.044 --> 18:00.012
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?
I'M OFF THE CASE.

18:00.046 --> 18:01.614
SUPERHEROES
NEVER GIVE UP.

18:01.648 --> 18:04.117
WE HAVE TO
SAVE THE WORLD EVERY TIME.

18:04.151 --> 18:07.820
YEAH, WELL,
I'M NO SUPERHERO.

18:07.854 --> 18:09.389
YOU MAY NOT
HAVE X-RAY VISION

18:09.422 --> 18:12.225
OR THE ABILITY TO LEAP TALL
BUILDINGS IN A SINGLE BOUND,

18:12.259 --> 18:14.827
BUT YOU HAVE SOME
PRETTY IMPRESSIVE CREDENTIALS.

18:14.861 --> 18:17.697
Daniel:
I'M DR. DANIEL PIERCE.

18:17.730 --> 18:19.499
I KNOW
EXACTLY WHO YOU ARE.

18:19.532 --> 18:21.601
I'M JUST A LITTLE UNCLEAR
AS TO WHAT THE FBI's PET SHRINK

18:21.634 --> 18:23.436
IS DOING
AT THE PUBLIC DEFENDERS' OFFICE.

18:23.470 --> 18:25.605
YOUR CLIENT
IS ACUTELY MENTALLY ILL.

18:25.638 --> 18:28.275
UNTIL HE GETS A COURT-ORDERED
FORENSIC MENTAL HEALTH EXAM,

18:28.308 --> 18:30.777
HE'S SANE
IN THE EYES OF THE LAW.

18:30.810 --> 18:32.111
I'VE MADE A REQUEST
TO THE JUDGE

18:32.145 --> 18:33.846
TO HAVE
A PSYCHIATRIST APPOINTED.

18:33.880 --> 18:35.348
I'LL DO IT.

18:35.382 --> 18:37.717
YOU'LL DO WHAT?

18:37.750 --> 18:39.619
EVALUATE BRADY,
TESTIFY ON HIS BEHALF.

18:39.652 --> 18:41.588
I'M SURE YOU'RE QUALIFIED,

18:41.621 --> 18:44.791
BUT THERE'S
A SLIGHT CONFLICT OF INTEREST.

18:44.824 --> 18:46.626
YOU'RE STILL
ON THE FBI's PAYROLL.

18:46.659 --> 18:49.962
I TOLD THEM BRADY DIDN'T DO IT.
THEY IGNORED MY EXPERT OPINION.

18:49.996 --> 18:52.465
NOW I'M OFFERING IT TO YOU...
FREE OF CHARGE.

18:52.499 --> 18:55.134
FBI's OWN EXPERT
TESTIFYING AGAINST THEM?

18:56.669 --> 18:58.805
HMM, I MEAN,
THAT'S THE KIND OF FIREWORKS

18:58.838 --> 19:00.907
I WOULD LOVE TO SET OFF
AT TRIAL.

19:00.940 --> 19:02.609
THERE MAY NOT BE A TRIAL.

19:02.642 --> 19:04.811
IF I CERTIFY THAT BRADY WAS TOO
ILL TO UNDERSTAND HIS RIGHTS,

19:04.844 --> 19:06.746
YOU MIGHT
GET THE CONFESSION THROWN OUT.

19:06.779 --> 19:09.148
HOW SOON CAN YOU SEE HIM?

19:09.182 --> 19:10.450
I HEARD THE CALL.

19:10.483 --> 19:12.185
YOU WERE HEARING VOICES?

19:12.219 --> 19:13.320
CALL, FALL,
BALL, WALL.

19:13.353 --> 19:15.054
WHAT DID THE VOICES SAY,
BRADY?

19:15.087 --> 19:18.491
THE SECRET FREQUENCY --
CODE OMEGA.

19:18.525 --> 19:19.926
WHAT WAS THE MESSAGE?

19:19.959 --> 19:21.594
I am called to be
the sword of justice.

19:21.628 --> 19:23.296
Vengeance is mine,
saith the Lord.

19:23.330 --> 19:25.398
The Lord is my shepherd.
I shall not want.

19:25.432 --> 19:27.066
BRADY -- I KNOW IT'S HARD,
BRADY, BUT TRY TO FOCUS.

19:27.099 --> 19:30.069
CAN YOU REMEMBER WHAT HAPPENED
THE NIGHT JUDGE TRENT DIED?

19:30.102 --> 19:31.771
I CAN'T.

19:31.804 --> 19:36.008
THE TURLOCK.
THEY'RE IN MY HEAD.

19:36.042 --> 19:38.345
THEY ARE SILENCING ME
WITH THEIR GAMMA RAY.

19:38.378 --> 19:39.512
STAY WITH ME.
SHE WAS STABBED, BRADY.

19:39.546 --> 19:41.147
WHAT CAN YOU TELL ME
ABOUT THAT?

19:41.180 --> 19:44.116
NOT THE SWORD OF JUSTICE,
THE DAGGER OF ISHTARION.

19:44.150 --> 19:47.520
BLACK OBSIDIAN,
VENGEANCE OF THE NIGHT SHADOWS,

19:47.554 --> 19:50.189
THE HERO'S BLOOD
RUNNETH LIKE A RIVER.

19:50.223 --> 19:52.425
WHAT HAPPENED, BRADY?

19:52.459 --> 19:55.094
THERE WAS BLOOD.
RED RED, DEAD DEAD.

19:55.127 --> 19:57.597
SHE FELL ON HER HEAD DEAD.

19:57.630 --> 19:59.599
[ GASPS ]

19:59.632 --> 20:01.534
GET OUT OF MY MIND!

20:01.568 --> 20:03.135
WHO ARE YOU TALKING TO?

20:03.169 --> 20:05.538
THEY'RE BLOCKING
THE FREQUENCIES!

20:05.572 --> 20:08.040
WAITSTOP, STOP, STOP!RADY!

20:08.074 --> 20:10.310
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:10.343 --> 20:12.144
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY.

20:12.178 --> 20:14.481
YOU'RE -- YOU'RE SAFE.

20:14.514 --> 20:16.583
[ Crying ] I'M SORRY.

20:18.184 --> 20:20.487
WHAT ARE YOU SORRY ABOUT?

20:23.523 --> 20:25.658
I KILLED HER.

20:32.599 --> 20:34.033
DOC,
YOU NEED TO SNAP OUT OF IT.

20:34.066 --> 20:35.668
YOU NEED TO
MIND YOUR OWN BUSINESS.

20:35.702 --> 20:37.537
YOU HAVEN'T LEFT THE HOUSE
IN THREE DAYS.

20:37.570 --> 20:39.406
I CAN'T
CANCEL ANY MORE CLASSES.

20:39.439 --> 20:42.575
DEAN HALEY'S NOT GONNA BUY
THE STOMACH VIRUS STORY FOREVER.

20:42.609 --> 20:44.677
AND I'VE GOT
A LOT OF MESSAGES FOR YOU.

20:44.711 --> 20:46.546
KATE'S BEEN CALLING,
AND THE PUBLIC DEFENDER.

20:46.579 --> 20:48.080
HE SAYS BRADY'S DOING BETTER
IN THE HOSPITAL,

20:48.114 --> 20:50.016
STABILIZING
ON THE MEDICATION.

20:51.451 --> 20:53.753
YOU HELPED BRADY, DOC.

20:53.786 --> 20:56.423
MAYBE IT'S TIME
TO HELP YOURSELF.

20:59.759 --> 21:02.762
LOOK,
I'M HERE IF YOU NEED ME.

21:07.634 --> 21:11.203
Natalie:
MAX IS RIGHT.

21:11.237 --> 21:12.905
YOU DID HELP BRADY.

21:12.939 --> 21:14.741
IF I'D GOT HIM
INTO THERAPY SOONER,

21:14.774 --> 21:16.042
THAT JUDGE
WOULD STILL BE ALIVE.

21:16.075 --> 21:19.111
YOU SHOULD HAVE
HAD HIM COMMITTED.

21:19.145 --> 21:21.448
GEE,
THANKS FOR THE PEP TALK.

21:21.481 --> 21:23.450
I'M NOT GONNA SUGAR-COAT IT.
IT'S A HORRIBLE SITUATION.

21:23.483 --> 21:26.052
YOU HERE IT COMES. IT.

21:26.085 --> 21:28.521
MAYBE SOMEONE ELSE
SHOULD BE MEDICATED

21:28.555 --> 21:30.056
MEDS, MEDS, MEDS, MEDS, MEDS.
BLAH, BLAH, BLAH, BLAH.

21:30.089 --> 21:31.558
IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT?
DO YOU WANT ME TO BE ON MEDS?

21:31.591 --> 21:33.059
THAT'LL
ALL MAKE YOU HAPPY?

21:33.092 --> 21:34.293
FINE.
I CAN DO THAT.

21:34.327 --> 21:36.629
MEDS ALL AROUND.

21:36.663 --> 21:38.965
I'M A DOCTOR.

21:40.967 --> 21:42.969
LEWICKI!

21:46.673 --> 21:49.609
I WANT
THAT PRESCRIPTION FILLED.

21:55.014 --> 21:57.316
OKAY.

21:57.350 --> 22:00.987
GOOD FOR YOU, DOC.
I'LL PICK IT UP RIGHT NOW.

22:01.020 --> 22:03.322
[ DOOR OPENS ]

22:03.356 --> 22:05.425
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

22:05.458 --> 22:07.093
IT'S A START.

22:07.126 --> 22:08.828
[ CHUCKLES ]
IT'S A START.

22:08.861 --> 22:11.330
WHAT DO -- WHAT MORE
DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

22:11.364 --> 22:12.665
ME? NOTHING.

22:12.699 --> 22:15.001
BRADY'S
A DIFFERENT STORY.

22:15.034 --> 22:16.636
HE'S STABILIZED NOW,

22:16.669 --> 22:18.838
WHICH MEANS THE REALITY
OF WHAT HE DID TO JUDGE TRENT

22:18.871 --> 22:20.172
IS PROBABLY HITTING HIM.

22:20.206 --> 22:22.108
MAYBE HE NEEDS A FRIEND.

22:22.141 --> 22:24.343
[ SIGHS ]

22:24.377 --> 22:26.679
Brady: I CAN'T
HEAR THE VOICES ANYMORE.

22:26.713 --> 22:29.015
I GUESS
THE MEDS ARE WORKING.

22:29.048 --> 22:33.152
BUT I CAN'T STOP THINKING ABOUT
WHAT I DID TO THE JUDGE.

22:33.185 --> 22:35.488
I SHOULD HAVE
GOT YOU HELP SOONER.

22:35.522 --> 22:36.623
YOU TRIED.

22:36.656 --> 22:40.460
I WAS TOO SICK
TO LISTEN.

22:40.493 --> 22:42.328
I WISH I HAD.

22:42.361 --> 22:44.697
YOU WANT TO
TALK ABOUT IT?

22:44.731 --> 22:47.366
IT SOUNDS SO STUPID NOW.

22:47.400 --> 22:51.303
I KNOW THE VOICES
WERE IN MY HEAD.

22:51.337 --> 22:54.006
BUT THEY SOUNDED SO REAL.

22:54.040 --> 22:58.177
AND THEY TOLD ME
THAT THE JUDGE WAS IN DANGER,

22:58.210 --> 23:00.513
THAT SHE
NEEDED MY PROTECTION.

23:00.547 --> 23:01.848
SO YOU WENT
TO THE HOUSE.

23:01.881 --> 23:03.282
YES.

23:03.315 --> 23:07.019
AND I TOOK MY SWORD,
LIKE THE VOICES TOLD ME,

23:07.053 --> 23:09.556
AND IT WAS LIKE
I WAS OUT OF MY BODY,

23:09.589 --> 23:12.559
LIKE I WAS ON THE CEILING
LOOKING DOWN.

23:12.592 --> 23:17.497
AND I SAW MYSELF
JUST STABBING HER OVER AND OVER.

23:17.530 --> 23:20.066
AND THERE WAS
SO MUCH BLOOD.

23:20.099 --> 23:24.737
AND THEN ALL OF A SUDDEN,
I'M KNEELING BESIDE HER,

23:24.771 --> 23:27.406
AND I PULLED THE KNIFE
FROM OUT OF HER,

23:27.440 --> 23:30.076
AND I TRIED TO
STOP THE BLEEDING,

23:30.109 --> 23:32.378
BUT IT WAS TOO LATE.

23:32.411 --> 23:35.682
I DON'T KNOW WHY I DID IT.

23:37.917 --> 23:39.385
I DIDN'T WANT TO
HURT HER.

23:39.418 --> 23:40.953
YOU WERE SICK, BRADY.

23:40.987 --> 23:44.123
YOU -- YOU DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT YOU WERE DOING.

23:46.793 --> 23:48.394
Nemesis:
AIN'T THAT THE TRUTH.

23:49.629 --> 23:50.930
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

23:54.100 --> 23:57.737
DR. PIERCE,
ARE YOU -- ARE YOU OKAY?

23:57.770 --> 23:59.906
IRONIC, ISN'T IT?
HE CAN'T SEE ME.

23:59.939 --> 24:01.107
HE'S TAKING HIS MEDS.

24:03.976 --> 24:09.048
DELUSIONS AND HALLUCINATIONS
WILL TRY TO MISLEAD US, BRADY.

24:09.081 --> 24:11.050
YES, THEY WILL.
BUT LET ME ASK YOU SOMETHING.

24:11.083 --> 24:14.787
DO YOU EVER THINK
YOU'RE HAVING A HALLUCINATION

24:14.821 --> 24:18.257
AND IT TURNS OUT TO BE REAL?

24:23.095 --> 24:24.697
BRADY,

24:24.731 --> 24:28.568
YOU SAID YOU TOOK THE SWORD
WITH YOU TO THE JUDGE'S HOUSE.

24:28.601 --> 24:30.302
THAT'S RIGHT.

24:30.336 --> 24:32.304
BUT YOU DIDN'T
KILL HER WITH IT.

24:32.338 --> 24:36.142
NO, I --
I USED THE KNIFE.

24:36.175 --> 24:37.844
WHERE DID YOU
GET THE KNIFE?

24:40.813 --> 24:43.950
I HAVE NO IDEA.

24:43.983 --> 24:47.119
Daniel: BRADY HAS
THE SWORD OF ELLEBRA,

24:47.153 --> 24:49.656
A WEAPON
HE COMPLETELY FETISHIZES.

24:49.689 --> 24:51.223
HE TAKES IT
TO THE JUDGE'S HOUSE,

24:51.257 --> 24:53.826
AND THEN HE KILLS HER
WITH SOME RANDOM KNIFE?

24:53.860 --> 24:55.528
WHAT ARE YOU GETTING AT?

24:55.562 --> 24:58.497
BRADY REMEMBERS PULLING THE
KNIFE OUT OF THE JUDGE'S CHEST

24:58.531 --> 25:00.800
AND TRYING TO SAVE HER
FROM HIS OWN PERSPECTIVE,

25:00.833 --> 25:02.602
BECAUSE THAT'S
WHAT HE ACTUALLY DID.

25:02.635 --> 25:04.336
BUT HE CAN ONLY REMEMBER
THE MURDER ITSELF

25:04.370 --> 25:07.674
AS IF HE WAS
WATCHING IT HAPPEN FROM --

25:07.707 --> 25:09.942
FROM OUTSIDE HIS BODY,
LIKE A FLY ON THE WALL.

25:09.976 --> 25:12.178
THAT'S BECAUSE
HE DIDN'T REALLY STAB HER.

25:12.211 --> 25:13.613
IT'S WHAT I WAS SAYING.
I WAS RIGHT.

25:13.646 --> 25:15.014
IT'S IMAGINATION INFLATION.

25:15.047 --> 25:16.683
THE AGENTS
INTERROGATING BRADY

25:16.716 --> 25:19.018
TOLD HIM HE STABBED THE JUDGE
WITH A KNIFE,

25:19.051 --> 25:21.187
SO THAT'S THE FALSE MEMORY
THAT HE FORMS,

25:21.220 --> 25:22.789
BUT HE DIDN'T
REALLY DO IT.

25:22.822 --> 25:24.691
THEN WHAT THE [BLEEP]
WAS HE DOING IN THAT HOUSE?

25:24.724 --> 25:28.695
HE WAS HEARING VOICES
TELLING HIM TO GO THERE,

25:28.728 --> 25:30.630
BUT WHAT IF THE VOICES
WEREN'T HALLUCINATIONS?

25:30.663 --> 25:32.331
WHAT IF THEY WERE REAL MESSAGES
FROM THE KILLER,

25:32.364 --> 25:34.867
SETTING BRADY UP
AS THE FALL GUY?

25:34.901 --> 25:36.836
HE'S SCHIZOPHRENIC.
HE'S THE PERFECT PATSY.

25:36.869 --> 25:40.372
DID ANYBODY CHECK HIS
PHONE RECORDS OR HIS E-MAIL?

25:40.406 --> 25:43.542
NO, THE CASE WAS CLOSED
AFTER BRADY CONFESSED.

25:43.576 --> 25:45.978
YOU SEE, I -- I --
MAYBE BRADY IS BEING SET UP.

25:46.012 --> 25:47.513
[ SIGHS ]

25:47.546 --> 25:49.381
WELL, IF YOU'RE RIGHT,
THE REAL KILLER WOULD BE SOMEONE

25:49.415 --> 25:51.884
WHO KNEW ABOUT BRADY'S FIXATION
WITH THE JUDGE.

25:51.918 --> 25:53.720
HER HUSBAND.

25:53.753 --> 25:55.722
HER HUSBAND! HE READ THE LETTERS
THAT SHE GOT FROM BRADY.

25:55.755 --> 25:57.523
HE WAS THERE
WHEN WE BRIEFED THE JUDGE.

25:57.556 --> 26:00.526
MNH-MNH, DAVID TRENT
WAS GIVING A SPEECH
IN FRONT OF 200 PEOPLE

26:00.559 --> 26:02.161
AT THE TIME
OF THE MURDER.

26:02.194 --> 26:03.996
THE PERFECT ALIBI

26:04.030 --> 26:06.365
IF YOU'VE HIRED SOMEBODY
TO KILL YOUR WIFE.

26:06.398 --> 26:08.334
I SUPPOSE SO,
BUT WHAT WAS HIS MOTIVE?

26:08.367 --> 26:09.669
I DON'T KNOW.

26:09.702 --> 26:11.904
HE -- HE--
HE WANTED INSURANCE MONEY.

26:11.938 --> 26:13.906
HE WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR.
I DON'T HAVE ALL THE ANSWERS.

26:13.940 --> 26:16.909
I JUST KNOW WE NEED TO
SEE THOSE PHONE RECORDS.

26:16.943 --> 26:21.547
Irene: YOU'RE BURNING
THE MIDNIGHT OIL, AGENT MORETTI.

26:21.580 --> 26:23.249
ANYTHING
I SHOULD KNOW ABOUT?

26:23.282 --> 26:24.884
I'M JUST WORKING UP
SOME NEW THEORIES

26:24.917 --> 26:26.585
ON THE JUDGE TRENT CASE.

26:26.619 --> 26:29.922
THAT CASE IS CLOSED, AND I DON'T
WANT YOU TRYING TO REOPEN IT.

26:29.956 --> 26:32.524
DR. PIERCE
THINKS IT'S POSSIBLE THAT BRA--

26:32.558 --> 26:35.094
HOW WELL DO YOU KNOW
PRETTY WELL.

26:35.127 --> 26:36.863
I WAS HIS STUDENT,

26:36.896 --> 26:38.865
AND WE'VE WORKED A LOT TOGETHER
OVER THE PAST FEW YEARS.

26:38.898 --> 26:40.032
AND HOW ABOUT
HIS PERSONAL LIFE?

26:40.066 --> 26:41.768
HE'S A PRIVATE PERSON.

26:41.801 --> 26:44.603
DID YOU KNOW HE HAS
A HISTORY OF MENTAL ILLNESS?

26:44.637 --> 26:46.272
YES.

26:46.305 --> 26:48.440
YES, BUT HIS CONDITION
IS STABLE,

26:48.474 --> 26:50.943
AND HIS MEDICAL HISTORY
IS CONFIDENTIAL.

26:50.977 --> 26:52.879
SO HOW DID YOU
KNOW ABOUT IT?

26:52.912 --> 26:54.613
IT'S MY RESPONSIBILITY
TO ENSURE

26:54.647 --> 26:57.449
THAT THE PEOPLE WHO WORK FOR
THIS OFFICE ARE FIT TO DO SO.

26:57.483 --> 26:59.886
DR. PIERCE IREALLY?

26:59.919 --> 27:01.120
AND WAS HE FINE
LAST YEAR?

27:01.153 --> 27:02.288
AS FAR AS I KNOW.

27:02.321 --> 27:03.622
BUT YOU WOULDN'T KNOW,
WOULD YOU?

27:03.656 --> 27:05.091
BECAUSE
YOU WERE IN WASHINGTON.

27:07.159 --> 27:08.795
WHAT'S THIS ALL ABOUT?

27:08.828 --> 27:11.964
WHY DON'T YOU ASK HIM?

27:21.073 --> 27:23.009
HEY.

27:25.011 --> 27:26.645
DID -- DID YOU GET
THE PHONE RECORDS?

27:26.679 --> 27:29.415
NO. WE'VE GOT SOMETHING ELSE
TO TALK ABOUT FIRST.

27:29.448 --> 27:30.817
WHEN I LEFT FOR D.C.,

27:30.850 --> 27:33.419
YOU QUIT YOUR CONSULTING GIG
WITH THE BUREAU.

27:33.452 --> 27:35.054
YEAH, SO?

27:35.087 --> 27:37.589
WHEN I ASKED YOU WHY, YOU NEVER
GAVE ME A STRAIGHT ANSWER.

27:37.623 --> 27:39.759
WHAT DOES THIS HAVE TO DO
WITH BRADY?

27:39.792 --> 27:41.894
TELL ME, DANIEL --
WHY DID YOU QUIT?

27:41.928 --> 27:44.663
WOW. WHAT IS -- WHAT IS THIS?
AN INQUISITION?

27:44.697 --> 27:46.598
I FOUND OUT
YOU STOPPED TEACHING, TOO.

27:46.632 --> 27:48.600
OH, YOU DID?
SO YOU'RE CHECKING UP ON ME?

27:48.634 --> 27:50.402
WELL, L-LET ME
SAVE YOU THE TROUBLE.

27:50.436 --> 27:52.171
I TOOK A SABBATICAL
TO WRITE A BOOK.

27:52.204 --> 27:54.506
MUST BE THE FIRST ONE YOU EVER
WROTE THAT DIDN'T GET PUBLISHED.

27:54.540 --> 27:55.908
TELL ME --
WHERE WERE YOU REALLY?

27:55.942 --> 27:59.578
I-I-IT --
TH-THAT'S NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

27:59.611 --> 28:03.750
CUT THE [BLEEP] DANIEL.
I NEED YOU TO TELL ME THE TRUTH.

28:09.989 --> 28:13.192
REXFORD
PSYCHIATRIC HOSPITAL.

28:16.228 --> 28:19.966
I, UH...
I WASN'T DOING VERY WELL.

28:19.999 --> 28:22.001
I REALIZED I NEEDED HELP,
SO I GOT IT.

28:23.635 --> 28:25.604
THEY MEDICATED ME.

28:25.637 --> 28:28.140
THAT'S WHERE I MET MAX.

28:28.174 --> 28:30.142
IN THE HOSPITAL.

28:30.176 --> 28:33.813
HE WAS AN ORDERLY.
HE WAS SMART.

28:33.846 --> 28:35.647
DIDN'T PUT UP
WITH ANY OF MY CRAP.

28:35.681 --> 28:38.818
WHEN I GOT STABILIZED, I DIDN'T
WANT TO STAY ON THE MEDS,

28:38.851 --> 28:40.987
BUT I KNEW I NEEDED SOMEONE
I COULD TRUST

28:41.020 --> 28:42.989
TO KEEP AN EYE ON ME,

28:43.022 --> 28:45.892
MAKE ME STICK TO MY SCHEDULE,
MY DIET.

28:45.925 --> 28:47.760
I PROMISED HIM
IF HE CAME BACK TO CHICAGO

28:47.794 --> 28:49.495
I'D GET HIM
A TEACHER'S ASSISTANTSHIP

28:49.528 --> 28:50.963
SO HE COULD
FINISH GRAD SCHOOL.

28:50.997 --> 28:54.166
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?

28:54.200 --> 28:57.003
I DIDN'T WANT YOU
TO THINK OF ME LIKE THAT.

28:57.036 --> 28:59.171
YOU KNOW, CRAZY.

28:59.205 --> 29:00.672
I WOULDN'T.

29:00.706 --> 29:02.674
YEAH, YOU WOULD.

29:02.708 --> 29:05.244
THAT'S WHY
I DON'T TALK ABOUT MY DIAGNOSIS,

29:05.277 --> 29:08.147
BECAUSE
THEN IT BECOMES WHO I AM.

29:08.180 --> 29:10.616
DANIEL,
I KNOW WHO YOU ARE.

29:13.552 --> 29:15.187
HOW'D YOU FIND OUT?

29:15.221 --> 29:17.256
REARDON.

29:17.289 --> 29:18.925
SHE RAN A BACKGROUND.

29:18.958 --> 29:20.592
[ CHUCKLES ]

29:20.626 --> 29:24.130
BIG BROTHER AT HIS FINEST,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

29:26.398 --> 29:28.700
I'M SORRY
I GOT YOU IN TROUBLE.

29:28.734 --> 29:30.636
YOU THINK I CARE ABOUT THAT,
DANIEL?

29:32.238 --> 29:34.073
I CARE ABOUT YOU.

29:38.044 --> 29:41.180
OKAY, WELL,
IF WE'RE DONE

29:41.213 --> 29:43.515
WITH EMBARRASSING
PERSONAL REVELATIONS 101,

29:43.549 --> 29:45.451
CAN WE GET BACK TO WORK?

29:47.920 --> 29:51.891
I'VE GOT A FRIEND IN I.T.B.
SHE OWES ME A FAVOR.

29:51.924 --> 29:55.061
SHE, UH, SLIPPED ME
BRADY McGRAW'S PHONE RECORDS.

29:55.094 --> 29:56.762
YOU WERE RIGHT.

29:56.795 --> 29:58.564
HE WAS GETTING PHONE CALLS
ON THE DAY OF THE MURDER --

29:58.597 --> 29:59.731
REAL ONES.

29:59.765 --> 30:01.233
FROM DAVID TRENT?

30:01.267 --> 30:02.969
DON'T KNOW.
WHO BOUGHT IT?

30:03.002 --> 30:06.072
NOT SURE, BUT MY FRIEND'S
PINGING THE PHONE AS WE SPEAK.

30:06.105 --> 30:08.540
SOMETIMES BIG BROTHER
AIN'T SO BAD.

30:08.574 --> 30:10.843
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ]

30:10.877 --> 30:13.245
Pete: HELLO?

30:14.613 --> 30:17.749
HELLO?

30:18.584 --> 30:21.653
[ SIGHS ]

30:21.687 --> 30:25.591
WHISKEY. UH, NEAT.

30:25.624 --> 30:27.426
BAD DAY?

30:27.459 --> 30:31.097
YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

30:31.130 --> 30:33.732
WELL, MAYBE
I CAN MAKE IT BETTER.

30:33.765 --> 30:37.436
OH, REALLY?

30:37.469 --> 30:39.838
[ LAUGHS ]
WHERE'S YOUR CAR?

30:39.872 --> 30:41.440
KatLOOKING PRETTY.AD.

30:41.473 --> 30:43.609
OH, SERIOUSLY?

30:43.642 --> 30:46.378
FBI.
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

30:46.412 --> 30:47.779
I THOUGHT WE WERE GONNA
GO TO YOUR PLACE.

30:47.813 --> 30:51.217
[ Laughing ]
IN YOUR DREAMS.

30:53.485 --> 30:55.988
[ GROANS ]

30:58.824 --> 31:01.293
NICE WORK, MATA HARI.
WHAT NOW?

31:01.327 --> 31:03.195
REARDON DIDN'T WANT ME
DIGGING BACK INTO THIS,

31:03.229 --> 31:04.964
SO I CAN'T
BRING A SUSPECT TO THE OFFICE

31:04.997 --> 31:06.465
UNTIL I'VE GOT
SOMETHING CONCRETE.

31:06.498 --> 31:07.967
SO,
WHERE ARE WE GOING?

31:08.000 --> 31:09.936
SOMEWHERE
WITH A LITTLE AMBIANCE.

31:11.070 --> 31:13.539
WHAT IS THIS PLACE?
THIS ISN'T -- THIS IS NOT LEGAL.

31:13.572 --> 31:16.208
DO I LOOK LIKE
I CARE ABOUT LEGAL?!

31:16.242 --> 31:19.411
I WASN'T LYING TO YOU ABOUT
THE LOUSY DAY THAT I'VE HAD.

31:19.445 --> 31:23.282
MY BOSS IS A RAGING [BLEEP]
I PROBABLY LOST MY JOB.

31:23.315 --> 31:25.651
THAT'S WHY YOU ARE HANDCUFFED
IN THIS DUMP,

31:25.684 --> 31:27.653
INSTEAD OF A NICE,
CLEAN INTERROGATION ROOM.

31:27.686 --> 31:29.655
I DIDN'T KILL THAT JUDGE.

31:29.688 --> 31:33.159
BUT YOU DID CALL BRADY MCGRAW.
THE PHONE RECORDS PROVE IT.

31:33.192 --> 31:35.727
MAKING A PHONE CALL
IS NOT A CRIME.

31:35.761 --> 31:38.064
CONSPIRACY
TO COMMIT MURDER IS.

31:38.097 --> 31:40.632
YOU TOLD BRADY
TO GO TO THAT HOUSE.

31:40.666 --> 31:43.435
THAT MAKES YOU RESPONSIBLE
FOR WHAT HAPPENED THERE.

31:43.469 --> 31:46.238
[ SIGHS ]

31:49.942 --> 31:51.577
IT WASN'T MY IDEA.

31:51.610 --> 31:54.013
I KNOW.
IT WAS DAVID TRENT'S.

31:54.046 --> 31:55.914
WHO THE [BLEEP]
IS DAVID TRENT?

31:59.051 --> 32:01.420
THEN WHO TOLD YOU
TO CALL BRADY?

32:04.223 --> 32:06.825
I'M NOT MESSING
AROUND HERE, PETE!

32:06.858 --> 32:10.997
I -- PLEASE.
I CAN'T SAY ANYTHING.

32:12.731 --> 32:16.102
[ SIGHS ]
HE'D -- HE'D KILL ME.

32:16.135 --> 32:18.537
OR THE GOVERNMENT WILL.
IT'S UP TO YOU.

32:18.570 --> 32:21.873
OKAY.

32:21.907 --> 32:25.211
I DIDN'T KNOW
ANYBODY WAS GONNA GET WHACKED.

32:25.244 --> 32:27.713
I SWEAR.

32:27.746 --> 32:31.383
HE JUST TOLD ME
TO CALL THIS CRAZY NUT,

32:31.417 --> 32:36.222
TALK ABOUT ALL THIS WEIRD STUFF
LIKE SWORDS AND ALIENS,

32:36.255 --> 32:38.690
AND GET HIM TO THE HOUSE.

32:38.724 --> 32:40.126
THAT'S IT.

32:40.159 --> 32:42.061
WHO TOLD YOU
TO CALL BRADY?

32:42.094 --> 32:45.464
[ SIGHS ]
BOBBY LONERGAN.

32:47.333 --> 32:50.169
I DON'T KNOW WHO THAT IS.

32:53.105 --> 32:56.075
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE,
AGENT MORETTI?

32:56.108 --> 32:57.743
MEET BOBBY LONERGAN.

32:57.776 --> 33:00.246
YOU'RE NEW TO CHICAGO,
SO YOU MAY NOT KNOW THIS,

33:00.279 --> 33:02.714
BUT HE'S ONE OF THE TOP GUYS
IN THE O'BANNION ORGANIZATION.

33:02.748 --> 33:05.317
REMEMBER WHEN I ASKED
FOR YOUR PERMISSION

33:05.351 --> 33:06.652
TO PURSUE OTHER SUSPECTS?

33:06.685 --> 33:08.387
I TOLD YOU
THAT THE IRISH MOB

33:08.420 --> 33:10.656
HAD A CONTRACT OUT
ON THE JUDGE LAST YEAR.

33:10.689 --> 33:13.392
I ALSO REMEMBER
DENYING YOUR REQUEST.

33:13.425 --> 33:14.760
OH, OKAY.

33:14.793 --> 33:16.462
UH, I CAN CUT HIM LOOSE,
BUT JUST SO YOU KNOW,

33:16.495 --> 33:17.996
I'VE GOT A WITNESS

33:18.030 --> 33:19.931
WHO SAYS THAT LONERGAN HERE
SET UP THE JUDGE'S MURDER.

33:19.965 --> 33:22.268
Bobby: I HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH JUDGE TRENT'S DEATH.

33:22.301 --> 33:23.835
THAT'S NOT
WHAT PETE DOLAN SAYS.

33:23.869 --> 33:25.537
PETE DOLAN'S A THUG

33:25.571 --> 33:28.040
WHO'LL TELL TALL TALES
ON ANYONE WHO BUYS HIM A DRINK.

33:28.074 --> 33:30.242
HE SEEMED PRETTY SOBER
WHEN HE GAVE YOU UP.

33:30.276 --> 33:31.943
REALLY?

33:31.977 --> 33:33.512
WELL, HIS SAINTED MOTHER'S
PRAYERS HAVE BEEN ANSWERED.

33:33.545 --> 33:34.746
I'LL CALL HER
WHEN I GET HOME.

33:34.780 --> 33:36.148
YOU'RE NOT GOING HOME.

33:36.182 --> 33:38.517
AND THE ONLY PERSON
YOU SHOULD CALL IS A LAWYER.

33:38.550 --> 33:40.252
I ALREADY TOLD YOU
I DON'T NEED ONE.

33:40.286 --> 33:43.789
I HAVE DONE NOTHING WRONG.
I AM A LEGITIMATE BUSINESSMAN.

33:43.822 --> 33:45.557
RIGHT.

33:45.591 --> 33:47.359
IF BY BUSINESS, YOU MEAN RUNNING
AN ORGANIZED CRIME SYNDICATE.

33:47.393 --> 33:48.960
[ LAUGHS ]

33:48.994 --> 33:50.962
THE JUDGE PUT AWAY FOUR
OF YOUR CRONIES ON RICO CHARGES.

33:50.996 --> 33:52.798
YOU FOUND OUT
SHE HAD A STALKER,

33:52.831 --> 33:55.801
SO YOU THOUGHT YOU'D USE HIM AS
A PATSY TO GET A LITTLE PAYBACK.

33:55.834 --> 33:58.470
ANY CRIMINAL AFFILIATIONS
I MAY HAVE HAD IN THE PAST --

33:58.504 --> 34:01.807
THEY WERE MERELY
YOUTHFUL INDISCRETIONS.

34:03.309 --> 34:05.744
I'M A REAL-ESTATE
INVESTOR NOW.

34:08.314 --> 34:11.550
WAIT HERE A MOMENT,
MR. LONERGAN.

34:11.583 --> 34:14.653
SURE.

34:14.686 --> 34:16.888
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

34:16.922 --> 34:19.057
WE'VE GOT THE RIGHT GUY.

34:19.091 --> 34:20.326
BUT THE WRONG MOTIVE.

34:26.732 --> 34:29.801
Kate: THANK YOU FOR COMING IN,
MR. TRENT.

34:29.835 --> 34:32.104
YOU MIND TELLING ME
WHAT I'M DOING HERE?

34:32.138 --> 34:34.973
WE JUST WANTED YOU TO KNOW
THAT WE'VE APPREHENDED THE MAN

34:35.006 --> 34:37.243
RESPONSIBLE
FOR YOUR WIFE'S MURDER.

34:38.844 --> 34:40.579
YOU DIDN'T NEED TO
DRAG ME ALL THE WAY DOWNTOWN

34:40.612 --> 34:42.214
TO TELL ME THAT.

34:42.248 --> 34:45.317
I WAS INFORMED THE MINUTE THAT
BRADY McGRAW WAS IN CUSTODY.

34:45.351 --> 34:47.119
Daniel:
BRADY'S INNOCENT.

34:47.153 --> 34:48.620
YOU'VE GOT SOME GALL,

34:48.654 --> 34:51.223
INTERRUPTING ME WHILE
I'M PLANNING MY WIFE'S FUNERAL

34:51.257 --> 34:52.758
TO START THAT CRAP AGAIN.

34:52.791 --> 34:55.727
Kate: WE DIDN'T MEAN TO
UPSET YOU, MR. TRENT.

34:55.761 --> 34:57.629
WE JUST WANTED YOU TO KNOW
THAT IT WAS BOBBY LONERGAN

34:57.663 --> 34:59.565
WHO ARRANGED
FOR YOUR WIFE'S DEATH.

34:59.598 --> 35:00.999
WHO?

35:01.032 --> 35:03.735
HE'S THE PRINCIPAL OWNER
OF KENMARE EQUITY GROUP.

35:03.769 --> 35:07.606
ACCORDING TO
YOUR S.E.C. FILINGS,

35:07.639 --> 35:09.841
KENMARE TOOK
A $2 MILLION DOLLAR STAKE

35:09.875 --> 35:12.010
IN YOUR REAL-ESTATE COMPANY
LAST YEAR.

35:12.043 --> 35:13.512
YES, THAT'S RIGHT.

35:13.545 --> 35:16.148
BUT I NEVER DEALT DIRECTLY
WITH THIS, UH, LONERGAN,

35:16.182 --> 35:17.849
YOU SAY HIS NAME WAS?

35:17.883 --> 35:21.019
YEAH, BUT, YOU SEE, REAL ESTATE
ISN'T THE ONLY BUSINESS

35:21.052 --> 35:22.454
THAT MR. LONERGAN IS IN.

35:22.488 --> 35:25.023
HE'S ALSO A SHOT-CALLER
FOR THE IRISH MOB,

35:25.056 --> 35:28.026
THE SAME ORGANIZATION THAT
THREATENED YOUR WIFE LAST YEAR.

35:28.059 --> 35:30.396
THEY KILLED HER?

35:34.466 --> 35:36.368
I'M SORRY I BLAMED YOU.

35:36.402 --> 35:38.036
I UNDERSTAND WHY YOU DID.

35:38.069 --> 35:41.807
YOU FILED FOR BANKRUPTCY
LAST YEAR CORRECT?

35:41.840 --> 35:43.475
YES, BUT I DON'T --
I DON'T SEE WHAT --

35:43.509 --> 35:45.043
AND THEN YOU WITHDREW
THE PETITION

35:45.076 --> 35:47.279
WHEN AFTER MR. LONERGAN
GAVE YOU THE $2 MIL.

35:47.313 --> 35:51.317
I NEEDED A CAPITAL INFUSION,
AND I GOT ONE.

35:51.350 --> 35:53.485
SURE, OF COURSE, BUT THE WEEK
AFTER HE MADE THE INVESTMENT,

35:53.519 --> 35:56.255
MR. LONERGAN BOUGHT UP
A BUNCH OF THE WORTHLESS LAND

35:56.288 --> 35:58.690
AROUND THE OLD
CABRINI-GREEN HOUSING PROJECT.

35:58.724 --> 36:01.460
I DON'T KNOW WHAT ANY OF THIS
HAS TO DO WITH MY WIFE'S DEATH.

36:01.493 --> 36:02.694
RIGHT AFTER
LONERGAN BOUGHT THAT LAND,

36:02.728 --> 36:04.430
YOUR WIFE MADE A RULING

36:04.463 --> 36:07.433
THAT APPROVED THE REZONING
OF THAT LAND FOR COMMERCIAL USE.

36:07.466 --> 36:09.167
LONERGAN
MADE MILLIONS OVERNIGHT.

36:09.201 --> 36:11.203
WITH A LITTLE HELP
FROM YOU. LUCKY.

36:11.237 --> 36:13.472
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

36:13.505 --> 36:15.707
YOU TIPPED HIM OFF
ABOUT YOUR WIFE'S RULING.

36:15.741 --> 36:18.477
THAT $2 MILLION WASN'T AN
INVESTMENT, IT WAS A KICKBACK.

36:18.510 --> 36:19.711
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

36:19.745 --> 36:21.847
WE HAVE MR. LONERGAN
IN CUSTODY.

36:21.880 --> 36:23.915
MURDER FOR HIRE
IS A DEATH-PENALTY OFFENSE.

36:23.949 --> 36:25.317
NOW, ONE OF YOU'S GONNA
TURN STATE'S EVIDENCE.

36:25.351 --> 36:27.653
THE OTHER'S
GONNA GET THE NEEDLE.

36:27.686 --> 36:30.021
JUST DEPENDS
ON WHO TALKS FIRST.

36:37.696 --> 36:39.698
[ SIGHS ]

36:45.771 --> 36:49.608
ONE NIGHT,
AFTER A FEW GLASSES OF WINE,

36:49.641 --> 36:52.110
KAREN TOLD ME
ABOUT A RULING SHE WAS MAKING

36:52.143 --> 36:54.613
IN THE CABRINI-GREEN
REZONING APPEAL.

36:54.646 --> 36:56.348
HMM.

36:56.382 --> 36:58.350
AND THE NEXT MORNING,

36:58.384 --> 37:00.552
SHE REALIZED
SHE HAD BEEN INDISCREET,

37:00.586 --> 37:02.721
AND SHE ASKED ME
NOT TO TELL ANYONE.

37:02.754 --> 37:04.390
BUT YOUR BUSINESS
WAS IN TROUBLE,

37:04.423 --> 37:06.358
AND HERE WAS AN OPPORTUNITY
TO MAKE A LITTLE MONEY.

37:06.392 --> 37:08.527
I HAD A DOZEN EMPLOYEES
WHO WERE GONNA LOSE THEIR JOB

37:08.560 --> 37:10.028
IF I WENT UNDER.

37:12.298 --> 37:16.468
SO I SOLD THE INFORMATION
TO LONERGAN.

37:16.502 --> 37:18.136
I DIDN'T SEE
THE HARM IT WOULD DO.

37:18.169 --> 37:21.039
BUT THEN YOUR WIFE WAS TAPPED
FOR SOLICITOR GENERAL.

37:21.072 --> 37:23.375
AND IF I CAN FIND THE MONEY
TRAIL BETWEEN YOU AND LONERGAN,

37:23.409 --> 37:24.576
IT CERTAINLY
WOULD HAVE COME UP

37:24.610 --> 37:26.044
DURING THE
BACKGROUND INVESTIGATION

37:26.077 --> 37:27.779
FOR YOUR WIFE'S
CONFIRMATION.

37:27.813 --> 37:30.416
YOU GO TO JAIL,
AND HER CAREER WOULD BE RUINED.

37:30.449 --> 37:33.919
LONERGAN CAME TO ME.

37:33.952 --> 37:35.587
AND HE SAID THAT
I NEEDED TO TAKE CARE OF IT,

37:35.621 --> 37:36.922
SO I WENT TO KAREN.

37:36.955 --> 37:38.424
TURN DOWN THE NOMINATION.

37:38.457 --> 37:40.426
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

37:40.459 --> 37:42.260
WE GOT A GOOD LIFE
HERE IN CHICAGO.

37:42.294 --> 37:43.995
IT'S SOLICITOR GENERAL,
DAVID.

37:44.029 --> 37:45.931
I'VE WORKED MY WHOLE LIFE
FOR THIS.

37:45.964 --> 37:48.900
Kate: DID YOU TELL HER WHY
YOU WANTED HER TO TURN IT DOWN?

37:48.934 --> 37:53.939
I KNEW SHE COULD NEVER
LIVE WITH THE DISHONESTY,

37:53.972 --> 37:56.942
AND THAT SHE WOULD WITHDRAW
HER NAME FROM CONSIDERATION

37:56.975 --> 38:00.145
AND -- AND -- AND -- AND
TELL ME TO TURN MYSELF IN.

38:02.614 --> 38:04.816
I DIDN'T WANT
HER CAREER DESTROYED.

38:04.850 --> 38:07.319
SO YOU JUST HAD HER KILLED
INSTEAD?

38:07.353 --> 38:10.121
NO! NO!
I NEVER WANTED THAT!

38:10.155 --> 38:11.957
I WENT TO LONERGAN.

38:11.990 --> 38:15.794
I NEED MORE TIME TO CONVINCE HER
TO TURN DOWN THE NOMINATION.

38:15.827 --> 38:17.128
IT'S TOO LATE.

38:17.162 --> 38:19.097
WE CAN'T RISK THIS COMING OUT,
DAVID.

38:19.130 --> 38:20.832
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT ELSE TO DO.

38:20.866 --> 38:22.033
JUST NEED TO BE CREATIVE.

38:22.067 --> 38:23.034
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

38:23.068 --> 38:24.836
ALL JUDGES MAKE ENEMIES.

38:24.870 --> 38:26.938
I'M SURE YOUR WIFE
HAS MORE THAN JUST A FEW.

38:26.972 --> 38:28.340
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

38:28.374 --> 38:30.609
I'M SAYING
SHE NEEDS TO GO.

38:30.642 --> 38:34.145
THE ONLY QUESTION IS WHETHER SHE
GOES ALONE OR YOU GO WITH HER.

38:39.585 --> 38:43.622
SO YOU TOLD HIM
ABOUT BRADY McGRAW.

38:43.655 --> 38:47.058
YOU KNEW HIS DELUSIONS WOULD
MAKE HIM THE PERFECT FALL GUY.

38:47.092 --> 38:49.961
I WANTED YOU
TO ARREST BRADY.

38:49.995 --> 38:51.963
THAT WAY, LONERGAN'S PLAN
WOULDN'T WORK,

38:51.997 --> 38:57.135
AND I'D HAVE HAD MORE TIME
TO CHANGE KAREN'S MIND.

38:57.168 --> 38:58.303
Kate: AND THEN
WHEN THAT DIDN'T HAPPEN,

38:58.336 --> 39:00.472
YOU REALIZED
YOU NEEDED AN ALIBI,

39:00.506 --> 39:01.940
AND LONERGAN
GOT HIS STOOGE

39:01.973 --> 39:03.575
TO LURE BRADY TO THE HOUSE
WITH THE CALLS.

39:03.609 --> 39:06.378
IT WAS A GREAT PLAN.

39:06.412 --> 39:09.014
AND IT WORKED OUT EVEN BETTER
THAN YOU COULD HAVE IMAGINED

39:09.047 --> 39:11.417
WHEN THE POOR GUY ACTUALLY
CONFESSED TO THE MURDER.

39:13.719 --> 39:15.387
IT WAS ALMOST
THE PERFECT CRIME.

39:20.225 --> 39:22.193
Daniel:
HOW ARE YOU DOING?

39:22.227 --> 39:23.595
I'M A LITTLE SCARED.

39:23.629 --> 39:25.096
TO LEAVE THE HOSPITAL.

39:25.130 --> 39:27.365
I DON'T KNOW
IF I CAN MAKE IT.

39:27.399 --> 39:28.900
YOU WILL.

39:28.934 --> 39:31.903
THANKS.

39:31.937 --> 39:33.805
BUT YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT IT'S LIKE.

39:35.907 --> 39:37.242
ACTUALLY, I DO.

39:38.810 --> 39:42.247
I WAS DIAGNOSED
WHEN I WAS 22.

39:43.815 --> 39:45.817
SO YOU'RE ON MEDS, TOO?

39:48.186 --> 39:51.156
THERE'S NO
ONE-SIZE-FITS-ALL TREATMENT.

39:51.189 --> 39:54.325
BUT WORK HELPS.

39:54.359 --> 39:57.529
AND, UH, FRIENDS.

40:00.265 --> 40:04.870
THE PERSON I CARED ABOUT MOST
WASN'T EVEN REAL.

40:04.903 --> 40:07.072
BUT I STILL MISS HER.

40:15.113 --> 40:18.083
Max: HEY, DOC.
DEAN HALEY CALLED.

40:18.116 --> 40:20.652
WANTED TO KNOW HOW
THE STOMACH FLU'S TREATING YOU.

40:20.686 --> 40:22.754
TELL HIM
I'VE MADE A FULL RECOVERY.

40:22.788 --> 40:24.389
I ALREADY DID.

40:24.422 --> 40:27.459
YOU'VE GOT BACK-TO-BACK MAKE-UP
CLASSES STARTING AT 10:00

40:27.493 --> 40:29.461
AND A FACULTY MEETING
OVER LUNCH.

40:29.495 --> 40:31.597
OH, AND I PICKED UP
YOUR PRESCRIPTION.

40:31.630 --> 40:33.064
IT'S RIGHT THERE
ON THE TABLE.

40:35.501 --> 40:36.835
GOOD FOR YOU, DOC.

40:36.868 --> 40:38.704
GOOD NIGHT, MAX.

