WHEN SHE'S GONE ♪

41:10.235 --> 41:16.374
♪ IT'S NOT WARM
WHEN SHE'S AWAY ♪

41:16.407 --> 41:20.378
♪ AIN'T NO SUNSHINE
WHEN SHE'S GONE ♪

41:20.411 --> 41:22.881
♪ SHE'S ALWAYS GONE TOO LONG

41:22.914 --> 41:28.720
♪ ANYTIME SHE GOES AWAY

41:28.754 --> 41:34.726
♪ WONDER THIS TIME
WHERE SHE'S GONE ♪

41:34.760 --> 41:38.564
♪ I WONDER
IF SHE'S GONE TO STAY ♪
